  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the effect of zinc supplementation in end stage renal
      failure on hemocystein level.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      hemocystein increased in end stage renal failure and zinc involved in hemocystein metabolism
      thus zinc supplementation may be effective on hemocystein level.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
