  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  hemodialysis for 3 months

          -  older than 18 years old

          -  serum level of zinc less than 72.6 microgram/ l in men and less than 70 microgram/ l
             in female

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  acute renal failre

          -  malabsorption

          -  history of steroid or cytotoxic consumption
      </textblock>
